{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people working like zombies and resigned to the fact that they're going-- not going to make-- make it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a terrible sight because every time we walked, and people would run-- start running so they can be shot, you know, so-- because they knew they will be shot.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, if there was a train that would come by, they would run and throw themselves in front of the train or trucks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was a constant-- there was a very morbid type of daily life because-- and-- and that's a place where I was beaten severely because I didn't-- I was so tired because sleep was not enough sleep.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the time you got up in the morning, and you cleaned up everything, and you worked an hour-- at least an hour-- to work, and after work-- the building, digging the tunnels-- and the-- and walk-- walk back to the camp, and-- so-- and then you had to clean up the camp, and do whatever they told you to.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was a very-- probably not much known about this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a horrible camp because this camp also didn't have crematoriums, but it had an open pit where they burned the bodies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was probably the most horrible smell because there was like an open fire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at night, they would take commanders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would say you, you, and you, and to take the bodies and carry him there and throw him into the pit.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Many times the SS troopers would take their rifle butts and push you in, and so there were screams.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People were burned alive, because they would hit him on the head and push him in or stab him, and-- and throw him into the fire.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
